#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/eic.rst:13
msgid ""
"You can visit the official link https://console.volcengine.com/eic and "
"deploy EIC KVCache on your compute cluster with web UI. In addition, we "
"provide particular image in volcano engine, which integrates various "
"optimizations based on the official image. You may use "
"tests/v1/storage_backend/test_eic.py to detect the connectivity of EIC."
msgstr ""

